Class ColoredVertex<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • homework2.ColoredVertex<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Filter, Pipe

    public class ColoredVertex<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A ColoredVertex is a vertex that has label T and a color VertexColor. A ColorVertex holds data regarding his parents and children labels T, and his outgoing and incoming edges labels T
